The guy brought a girl to his place. We drank, danced, went to bed to have sex. The guy put the girl on her back, and himself on top. He watches her for half an hour, an hour, two, three hours, after which he gets up from her and says:
- That's it! Now you won't see me for a long time.
The girl clarifies:
- Should I leave already?
The guy to her:
- Turn over on your stomach!
